preference.name: TCIC_co_warn_link_types
preference.preference_description: Defines the list of link types between a source object and its target. Use the TCIC_co_warn_on_linked_doc preference to display a warning message during Check Out, if necessary, based on the links defined in this preference. Available Link Types: - To manage catia link type REF- REF: Content of CATIA_mml_link_type - To manage catia link type Ref-Inst: Content of CATIA_mmlassy_link_type - To manage catia link type DWG: Content of CATIA_drawing_link_type - To manage catia link type Process: Content of CATIA_manufacturing_link_type - To manage catia link type Analysis: Content of CATIA_analysis_link_type - To manage catia link type Flattening: Content of CATIA_flattening_link_type All others values are ignored
